from Dead-End that where to charred to use. "Gooood, you brought it" the
Quintesson said, switching head again. "Uhhh yeah" replied Wildrider, "You
better not try anything funny" he accused the Quintesson. "Ohhh no, I wont,
but he suffered very serious heat burns from energy, and some of his body
needs to be replaced completely" he said, getting back to work.
